## For Claude Code / Cursor / Codex Implementation
### Target: `rtmendes/ad-campaign-engine` (Convex + React + Tailwind + shadcn/ui)

---

## Executive Summary

Build a full AdRoast clone ("Creative Roast") into the existing Ad Campaign Engine at `adengine.insightprofit.live`. This adds **pre-launch creative scoring**, **competitor creative spy**, **AI-improved variant generation**, and **brand kit management** — the 4 capabilities we currently lack. The module uses Claude Vision for creative analysis, GPT Image 2 for variant generation, and Meta Ad Library API for competitor creative intelligence.

**What we're building:**
- 4 roast/analysis modes (Standard, Winners Benchmark, Competitor Spy, Meta Performance)
- Pre-launch creative scoring engine (0-100 score with category breakdowns)
- AI creative improvement engine (generates 3 improved variants with predicted lift)
- Brand kit management (auto-extract brand assets from URL)
- Lazy mode (zero-context auto-analysis)
- Project management (save, search, compare analyses)
- Credit-free (we own the infrastructure — unlimited internal use)

**What we're NOT building:**
- Payment/billing system (internal tool)
- User auth tiers (already have auth)
- Credit limits (unlimited for our team)

---

## 1. INFORMATION ARCHITECTURE

### 1.1 New Pages (4)

```
/roast              → Main Roast Dashboard (new analysis + project list)
/roast/:id          → Individual Roast Result page
/brand-kits         → Brand Kit Manager
/competitor-intel   → Competitor Creative Intelligence (enhanced spy)
```

### 1.2 New Convex Tables (6)

```
roastAnalyses       → Individual roast/analysis records
roastVariants       → AI-generated improved variants per analysis
brandKits           → Brand kits (colors, logo, fonts, voice)
competitorCreatives → Pulled competitor ad creatives
roastProjects       → Project folders for organizing analyses
roastTemplates      → Saved context templates for quick re-roast
```

### 1.3 New Backend Modules (8)

```
convex/roast/schema.ts           → Table definitions
convex/roast/analyzeCreative.ts  → Main AI analysis action
convex/roast/generateVariants.ts → AI variant generation action
convex/roast/brandKitExtractor.ts → URL → brand assets extraction
convex/roast/competitorPull.ts   → Meta Ad Library API integration
convex/roast/scoringFramework.ts → Scoring rubric engine
convex/roast/queries.ts          → All read queries
convex/roast/mutations.ts        → All write mutations
```

### 1.4 New Frontend Components (18)

```
src/pages/RoastPage.tsx               → Main roast dashboard
src/pages/RoastResultPage.tsx         → Individual result view
src/pages/BrandKitsPage.tsx           → Brand kit manager
src/pages/CompetitorIntelPage.tsx     → Enhanced competitor spy

src/components/roast/CreativeDropzone.tsx    → Drag-drop upload
src/components/roast/RoastModeSelector.tsx   → 4-mode card selector
src/components/roast/ContextForm.tsx         → Mandatory + optional fields
src/components/roast/LazyModeToggle.tsx      → Lazy mode switch
src/components/roast/BrandSelector.tsx       → Pick brand kit
src/components/roast/WinnerUploader.tsx      → Upload 1-10 winners
src/components/roast/CompetitorFields.tsx    → Competitor name + URL + FIND ADS
src/components/roast/ScoreGauge.tsx          → Animated radial score 0-100
src/components/roast/CategoryBreakdown.tsx   → Score breakdown by category
src/components/roast/WeakSpotsList.tsx       → Identified issues + fixes
src/components/roast/VariantGallery.tsx      → A/B/C improved variants
src/components/roast/LiftBadge.tsx           → Predicted lift percentage
src/components/roast/ProjectSidebar.tsx      → Project list + search
src/components/roast/BrandKitCard.tsx        → Brand kit display/edit
