### 7.5 Design System

Match existing Ad Campaign Engine design system:
- **Colors:** Dark theme (`bg-zinc-950`, `text-zinc-100`)
- **Accent:** Brand gold/amber for score highlights
- **Cards:** `bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl`
- **Buttons:** Primary = amber/gold solid, Secondary = zinc-800 outline
- **Score gauge:** Animated SVG radial gauge with color gradient (red→yellow→green)
- **Category bars:** Horizontal progress bars with category-specific colors
- **Severity badges:** 🔴 Critical = `bg-red-500/10 text-red-400`, 🟡 Major = `bg-yellow-500/10 text-yellow-400`, 🟢 Minor = `bg-green-500/10 text-green-400`
- **Lazy mode toggle:** Custom switch component with ⚡ icon

